{"tid":137771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認真問著yeezy係咩心態","createTime":"2017-02-28T05:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T07:36:02.000Z","uid":88143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fa1b5b13e059715dabca0b139e606fce4fb6302","tid":137771,"uid":88143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"眼見好多人都著或者想搶yeezy <br />\n但其實係真心覺得靚定係盲跟潮流？<br />\n見到網上學生哥或者冇乜錢個d都死慳死抵要買<br />\n買完又驚係假上網係咁問 都係對鞋啫唔洗緊張下嘛<br />\n俾5，6千蚊買炒價adidas 不如買對一線牌子波鞋好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖則我都知大把有錢人都係會著yeezy 但識好多冇錢又想威既人 <br />\n搵萬零蚊買對幾千數既鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 非潮流撚 純粹想知"},{"pid":"b110c0a367b830564e69c1dcfc566fe3f3b3259e","tid":137771,"uid":54104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"其實好撚柒"},{"pid":"4756bb061b4ed06a4b24e668497349bfd4076f45","tid":137771,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"身份象徵"},{"pid":"439ed5f14760778e6f2e88896b87b15786a9a53b","tid":137771,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身份象徵</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係柒下柒下嘅身份"},{"pid":"af49f33c24dbbe3d52fd689028f9338c10d5e0bf","tid":137771,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:43:47.000Z","msg":"旺角搵個咩LV呀姐個袋已經買到十對鞋<br />\n幾千蚊真係唔知有咩好晒"},{"pid":"54c3fb78d1827293b487b502fc156aa4698ca3ca","tid":137771,"uid":71473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"有閑錢又覺得靚買黎著冇問題<br />\n不過呢班學生哥心態就好有問題"},{"pid":"2493a9225d46a3bccd751a0653813a70370cf7d8","tid":137771,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"我對鞋個樣其實好柒,不過幾舒服"},{"pid":"8b78d92d18744391e11d1fed68fba6bbc682e4f9","tid":137771,